            <td colspan="2"><strong>Subfield Codes</strong><br></td>
         </tr>
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td colspan="1">$a - Statement of scale (NR) <br>$b - Statement of projection (NR) <br>$c - Statement of coordinates (NR) <br>$d - Statement of zone (NR) <br>$e - Statement of equinox (NR) <br></td>
            <td colspan="1">$f - Outer G-ring coordinate pairs (NR) <br>$g - Exclusion G-ring coordinate pairs (NR) <br>$6 - Linkage (NR) <br>$8 - Field link and sequence number (R) <br></td>
